<h3>2. But SMBs running paid search are satisfied with results</h3>
<p>When it comes to how satisfied small businesses are with their marketing investments, search advertising was one of the top tactics they were pleased withâ€”behind video marketing and advertising and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/reputation-management">reputation management</a>.</p>
<p>Search advertising is effective at <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/01/12/how-to-generate-leads">driving leads</a> and can be pretty easy to measure and tie back to ROI, so itâ€™s not a surprise to see it so high on the list.</p>
