<p>The show breaks down AI news, with a strong bent towards how it affects marketing. Even though itâ€™s a current events format, there is a lot of actionable information you can use. For example, Paul and Mike often discuss the impacts of new AI tech that is useful in marketing.</p>
<div id="breaking-b2b"></div>
<h3>8. Breaking B2B</h3>
