<p>But this commercial shifts focus and takes a different tone entirely, and itâ€™s clearly targeting a different audience. The emergency medical providers at the motorsport racing track pictured count on their well-fitting, durable gear not to inhibit their movement when seconds matter most. With this spot, FIGS highlights its durability, comfort, and reliabilityâ€”and the grave impact of scrubs that fall short on any of these.</p>
