										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It&#8217;s hard to imagine a time in B2B marketing history when everything changed this quickly.</p>
<p>Just in the last couple of years, we&#8217;ve seen incredibly volatile Google SERPS, entire job categories created (AI prompt engineer?), and hundreds of new tools and features just waiting for us to learn.</p>
<p>The one theme running through the B2B marketing trends for 2025 is a continuation of this evolution. But with change comes opportunity. Marketers who plan for what&#8217;s coming will take giant leaps ahead of their competitors.</p>
<h3>Contents</h3>
